液得作為 A施用毒品之證據，試問：刑警甲應踐行如何的正當法律程序
始得對 A採取尿液？A對採取尿液的處分，有無聲明不服的救濟管道？
（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "66f1ef574869", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113170", "c": "103", "s": "0204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "刑法與刑事訴訟法實務", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年警察人員升官等考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "policepromo", "civil_category": "海岸巡防人員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-00004', 'policepromo-f410f0c7', 'policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-113-a9c8f8e6', 'sub-policepromo-f410f0c7-01', NULL, 'essay', '承上題，刑警甲對 A詢問前，告知 A得選任辯護人後，A立即表示要選
任律師為辯護人，刑警甲應如何處理？假如刑警甲不理會 A的表示要選
任辯護人，逕行詢問，在詢問中，A的辯護人 B律師火速趕到警察局，
要求立即接見，刑警甲應如何處理？假如刑警甲禁止辯護人 B律師在場
及筆記，A對刑警甲之禁止處分，有無聲明不服的救濟管道？（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "66f1ef574869", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113170", "c": "103", "s": "0204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "刑法與刑事訴訟法實務", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年警察人員升官等考試", "original_question_number": "四", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "policepromo", "civil_category": "海岸巡防人員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-00005', 'policepromo-f410f0c7', 'policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-113-c1c64de5', 'sub-policepromo-f410f0c7-02', NULL, 'essay', 'A國為限制外國軍艦行經其領海，特別規定軍艦行經領海必須獲得其事
先同意。今 B國派遣隸屬於其海軍之科學研究船逕自行經 A國領海，B
國主張其為無害通行，A國則主張應經其事先同意。試依據《聯合國海
洋法公約》論述A國和 B國主張之合法性。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4f851f52350d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113170", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "國際海洋法", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年警察人員升官等考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "policepromo", "civil_category": "海岸巡防人員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-00006', 'policepromo-f410f0c7', 'policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-113-c1c64de5', 'sub-policepromo-f410f0c7-02', NULL, 'essay', 'C 國為發展攻擊性武器，於公海劃定一海域，進行武器試驗，由於該海
域漁業資源豐富，是鄰近國家 D 國之重要漁場，因此 D 國指控 C 國違
反《聯合國海洋法公約》。試依據前述公約，分析 C 國行為之合法性。
（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4f851f52350d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113170", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "國際海洋法", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年警察人員升官等考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "policepromo", "civil_category": "海岸巡防人員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-00007', 'policepromo-f410f0c7', 'policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-113-c1c64de5', 'sub-policepromo-f410f0c7-02', NULL, 'essay', 'E 國和 F 國均為《聯合國海洋法公約》締約方，兩國海域間存有一主權
爭議島嶼，儘管該島面積小，亦無淡水，鮮少有植物生長。為強化對於
該島之控制和管轄，E 國透過其海域執法，於該島周遭 200 浬內扣押當
時在該海域捕魚之 F國籍漁船，逮捕相關人員，拒不釋放。試問F國應
如何尋求救濟？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4f851f52350d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113170", "c": "103", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "國際海洋法", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年警察人員升官等考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "policepromo", "civil_category": "海岸巡防人員"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-00008', 'policepromo-f410f0c7', 'policepromo-f410f0c7-moex-113-c1c64de5', 'sub-policepromo-f410f0c7-02', NULL, 'essay', 'G國為探測和調查管轄海域內之水文和漁業資源，於相關水域放置相關
